      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "🧭  EXPLORER\n(Default tier at sign-up)\n\nAlready built:\n✅  / (homepage)\n✅  Access to Academy app\n\nPending port (boss called out):\n🆕  Finternship Orientation\n🆕  Financial Planning Basics\n🆕  Advisory Fundamentals\n🆕  Orientation videos (modules 1–4)\n\nExit path:\n🆕  \"Request upgrade to Papers\"",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "explorer",
      "originalText": "🧭  EXPLORER\n(Default tier at sign-up)\n\nAlready built:\n✅  / (homepage)\n✅  Access to Academy app\n\nPending port (boss called out):\n🆕  Finternship Orientation\n🆕  Financial Planning Basics\n🆕  Advisory Fundamentals\n🆕  Orientation videos (modules 1–4)\n\nExit path:\n🆕  \"Request upgrade to Papers\"",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
