      "isDeleted": false,
      "boundElements": null,
      "updated": 1,
      "link": null,
      "locked": false,
      "fontSize": 18,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "📚  PAPERS-TAKER\n(Everything Explorer has, plus:)\n\nAlready built in Academy:\n✅  /learning-track/pre-rnf (phased track)\n✅  /cmfas-exams + 5 modules\n✅  All Product Categories (6 AIA products)\n✅  /question-banks + Study Banks\n✅  Exam per product (scored)\n✅  /roleplay (Tavus AI coach)\n\nAlready ported from Skool:\n✅  Supplementary Training\n✅  Product Knowledge\n✅  Sales training\n✅  Appointment Setting\n✅  Ghost Map / Ghost Sniper\n\nPending port (boss called out):\n🆕  Financial Cert Sponsorship\n🆕  Must Read Books\n🆕  Soft Skills 1.0\n\nExit path:\n🆕  \"Request upgrade to Post-RNF\"",
      "textAlign": "center",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "papers",
      "originalText": "📚  PAPERS-TAKER\n(Everything Explorer has, plus:)\n\nAlready built in Academy:\n✅  /learning-track/pre-rnf (phased track)\n✅  /cmfas-exams + 5 modules\n✅  All Product Categories (6 AIA products)\n✅  /question-banks + Study Banks\n✅  Exam per product (scored)\n✅  /roleplay (Tavus AI coach)\n\nAlready ported from Skool:\n✅  Supplementary Training\n✅  Product Knowledge\n✅  Sales training\n✅  Appointment Setting\n✅  Ghost Map / Ghost Sniper\n\nPending port (boss called out):\n🆕  Financial Cert Sponsorship\n🆕  Must Read Books\n🆕  Soft Skills 1.0\n\nExit path:\n🆕  \"Request upgrade to Post-RNF\"",
      "lineHeight": 1.25,
