      "originalText": "✅  EXISTING ADMIN TABS\n\n• User Management (directory, bulk actions, approvals)\n• Video Progress\n• Performance\n    — Quizzes (all users + takers/non-takers filter)\n    — Study Progress (mastery, at-risk flags, leaderboard)\n• Question Bank Manager (CRUD on study + exam questions)\n• Leaderboard (Pro Achiever exam)\n• Feedback\n\nLearning Track admin (separate sub-app)\n• Roster · Heatmap · Submissions · Activity · Phase controls",
