      "fontSize": 20,
      "fontFamily": 1,
      "text": "🆕  VISION — TO BUILD\n\n• Tier Upgrade Requests queue (approve/reject)\n• Manual tier assignment in User Management\n    — Move users between Explorer / Papers / Post-RNF\n• Unlock / prerequisite config per learning item\n• Persona-specific reporting (mastery by tier)\n• Signup auto-assign default tier = Explorer\n\nBigger picture:\n• Retire Skool → Academy single front door\n• Port remaining Skool classrooms (see list above)\n• Tier-aware nav, home pages, and email/nudge logic",
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "containerId": "adminVision",
      "originalText": "🆕  VISION — TO BUILD\n\n• Tier Upgrade Requests queue (approve/reject)\n• Manual tier assignment in User Management\n    — Move users between Explorer / Papers / Post-RNF\n• Unlock / prerequisite config per learning item\n• Persona-specific reporting (mastery by tier)\n• Signup auto-assign default tier = Explorer\n\nBigger picture:\n• Retire Skool → Academy single front door\n• Port remaining Skool classrooms (see list above)\n• Tier-aware nav, home pages, and email/nudge logic",
